🌳 Branching and Merging
	Create a branch: git branch <name>
	Switch branch: git checkout <name> or git switch
	Create & switch: git checkout -b <name>
	Merge: git merge <branch>
	Rebase: git rebase <branch>
	git stash, git stash pop

🗂️ Remote Repositories
	Add remote: git remote add origin <url>
	View remotes: git remote -v
	Push branch: git push origin <branch>
	Set upstream: git push -u origin <branch>

🛠️ Undoing Changes
	git reset vs git revert
	Unstage file: git reset <file>
	Discard changes: git checkout -- <file>
	Revert commit: git revert <commit_hash>
	Hard reset: git reset --hard <commit_hash>

